The paper deals with the problem of cell association and service scheduling in femtocell networks, which is a topic related to network optimization and management. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves the use of algorithms and optimization techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The consideration of open and closed access strategies and the aim to minimize latency could also indicate a connection to cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
